{"tid":1284760,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港元續強勢 兌美元創自17年5月新高 兌日圓報7.227","createTime":"2019-07-04T10:01:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T14:22:52.000Z","uid":58669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9bd6b9cf8223b97541298dc44f5f23b016904095","tid":1284760,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:01:48.000Z","msg":"百威亞太會從明日起招股，並有機會成為今年全球最大集資額的新股。在大型新股招股活動，加上內地企業派息高峰期影響下，港匯進一步轉強，其中兌美元7.7855，為2017年5月19日以來新高。最新報7.7875，升102點子。<br />\n<br />\n港元兌日圓今日亦上揚，每百日圓兌美元，最新報7.227。<br />\n<br />\n港元兌英鎊及歐元均上揚，英鎊兌港元最新報9.7977，歐元兌港元最新報8.7864。<br />\n<br />\n點擊瀏覽《香港01》更多內容和圖集<br />\n<br />\n你可能感興趣： <br />\n百威亞太招股在即 短期拆息上揚 1個月息見2.7厘創海嘯後新高<br />\n港元轉強 兌美元升穿7.8 兌日圓曾高見7.1934<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/港元續強勢-兌美元創自17年5月新高-兌日圓報7-227-025111817.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E7%BA%8C%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%A2-%E5%85%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E5%89%B5%E8%87%AA17%E5%B9%B45%E6%9C%88%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E5%85%8C%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93%E5%A0%B17-227-025111817.html&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFIyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=96c74632\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/港元續強勢-兌美元創自17年5月新高-兌日圓報7-227-025111817.html</a>"},{"pid":"d95beb7209dcb1981de9a0cb9a7b7691bcd4c7b8","tid":1284760,"uid":27946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"發夢見到港紙越黎越危<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cc39cac2a356c97ff98d5a2101cb023484ec54","tid":1284760,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d95beb7209dcb1981de9a0cb9a7b7691bcd4c7b8","tid":1284760,"uid":27946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"發夢見到港紙越黎越危<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:39:31.000Z","msg":"港紙做咩無啦啦走強？"},{"pid":"c0a2728b26d59deda17aa4d6f04a195b352f8d22","tid":1284760,"uid":